sentences: Born in Little Rock, Arkansas, he signed with Secretly Canadian in 2014.
The album is a "movement towards a distinctive and immersive preview of R&B, reminiscent of other innovative R&B artists Frank Ocean and The Weeknd."
Following the success of his 3 track EP LATE, Clark released his first full-length album on the Secretly Canadian roster, The Lonely Roller in 2015.
Clark is currently on tour with Sinkane promoting his new album.
